## Database Patterns

### Snowflake Schema Architecture

```sql
-- RAG-optimized schema
CREATE SCHEMA RAG_SCHEMA;

CREATE TABLE RAG_SCHEMA.PROPERTIES (
    property_id VARCHAR,
    tenant_id VARCHAR,
    name VARCHAR,
    address VARCHAR,
    property_type VARCHAR,
    acquisition_date DATE,
    purchase_price NUMERIC(15,2),
    current_valuation NUMERIC(15,2),
    noi NUMERIC(15,2),
    cap_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (property_id, tenant_id)
);

CREATE TABLE RAG_SCHEMA.FINANCIAL_METRICS (
    metric_id VARCHAR,
    property_id VARCHAR,
    tenant_id VARCHAR,
    month DATE,
    revenue NUMERIC(15,2),
    expenses NUMERIC(15,2),
    noi NUMERIC(15,2),
    occupancy_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (metric_id)
);

-- Materialized View for common aggregations
CREATE MATERIALIZED VIEW RAG_SCHEMA.PROPERTY_PERFORMANCE AS
SELECT 
    p.property_id,
    p.tenant_id,
    p.name,
    COUNT(*) as transaction_count,
    AVG(fm.noi) as avg_noi,
    AVG(fm.occupancy_rate) as avg_occupancy,
    MAX(fm.month) as latest_month
FROM RAG_SCHEMA.PROPERTIES p
LEFT JOIN RAG_SCHEMA.FINANCIAL_METRICS fm 
    ON p.property_id = fm.property_id
GROUP BY p.property_id, p.tenant_id, p.name;
```

### PostgreSQL/Supabase Schema

```sql
-- OLTP schema for user data, embeddings, RLS
CREATE TABLE public.users (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    tenant_id UUID REFERENCES tenants(id),
    email TEXT UNIQUE,
    full_name TEXT,
    role TEXT CHECK (role IN ('admin', 'analyst', 'viewer')),
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now(),
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE TABLE public.properties_embeddings (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    property_id VARCHAR,
    tenant_id UUID REFERENCES tenants(id),
    embedding vector(1024),
    embedding_model TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now(),
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT now()
);

-- Enable RLS
ALTER TABLE public.users ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;
CREATE POLICY "Users can view own tenant data"
    ON public.users
    FOR SELECT
    USING (tenant_id = (SELECT tenant_id FROM public.users WHERE id = auth.uid()));
```

### Query Best Practices
- Use parameterized queries always (prevent SQL injection)
- Leverage Snowflake query result cache
- Batch operations for embeddings (1000 records per batch)
- Index on tenant_id and date ranges
- Partition large tables by date/tenant

