## Authentication & Authorization

### Clerk Integration
```python
from src.core.security import get_current_user

@app.post("/api/portfolio")
async def create_portfolio(
    req: PortfolioCreate,
    user: User = Depends(get_current_user)
):
    """Create new portfolio. Only accessible to portfolio managers."""
    if user.role not in ["admin", "portfolio_manager"]:
        raise UnauthorizedError(f"User {user.id} lacks required role")
    
    return await portfolio_service.create(req, tenant_id=user.tenant_id)
```

### RBAC Levels
- **admin**: Full access, user management, billing
- **portfolio_manager**: CRUD on portfolio, view all team data
- **analyst**: Create/read queries, view assigned portfolios
- **viewer**: Read-only access

