## Deployment & DevOps

### Environment Management
- `.env.example`: Template with all vars
- Vercel for Next.js (auto-deploys from main)
- FastAPI service: Docker container on Cloud Run / Railway
- Snowflake: Cloud-hosted (no deployment needed)
- Supabase: Cloud-hosted (migrations via scripts)

### Monitoring
- Log aggregation: JSON-structured logs to CloudLogging
- Metrics: Track query latency, cache hit rates, token usage
- Alerts: PagerDuty for critical errors
- Profiling: Track slow queries, embedding generation

### Database Migrations
```bash
# Create migration
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Add column"

# Apply migrations
alembic upgrade head

# Rollback
alembic downgrade -1
```

